### 1. 상품 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2.1. 상품 단건 조회 - 상품 ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/products?productId={productId}
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2.2. 상품 단건 조회 - 회사 ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/products?companyId={companyId}
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2.3. 상품 단건 조회 - 상품 이름
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/products?productName=먹태깡
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json